{"id":"c5f343bdf7fefa19b9700148","title":"10 Fast Fishers","slug":"10-fast-fishers","event":{"name":"FCSC 2026","year":2026},"event_name":"FCSC 2026","year":2026,"category":"web","raw_category":"web","tags":[],"difficulty":"1/5","description":"Tu penses écrire rapidement sur ton clavier ? Prouve-le dans10 Fast Fishers— le jeu de frappe sous-marin addictif où vitesse et style se rencontrent !Regarde des poissons colorés nager sur ton écran, chacun portant un mot. Tape vite, associe le mot, clique sur le poisson, et regarde ton document se transformer sous tes yeux. Poissons-globes en gras, poissons-anges en italique, et même des méduses sournoises qui vont chambouler ta mise en forme !Enchaîne les combos, accumule les points, et deviens le plus grand dactylographe des océans. Mais méfie-toi du calamar… 🦑Prêt à faire des vagues ? Les crevettes t’attendent !","has_source":true,"files":[{"path":"10-fast-fishers.tar.xz","sha256":"48dfbf44c0eae54f970eb5c3119d08b570f34536cd1a7ab5e7a121a227839664","size":11076,"is_source":true,"lfs":false},{"path":"docker-compose.yml","sha256":"d458d03459b4f9e76564f0267b46303f17b516421383f99780a4606ea509102d","size":272,"is_source":true,"lfs":false},{"path":"writeups/writeup_00.html","sha256":"f4bc41f8691497ac34e158fce7da3a4563331e50a1c9f0b654f79979d8f40a0b","size":213693,"is_source":true,"lfs":false}],"solve_languages":[],"docker":true,"writeups":[{"url":"https://hackropole.fr/en/writeups/fcsc2026-web-10-fast-fisher/0472a24d-94d8-4b3a-a5b4-f70ead070b93/","origin":"hackropole","is_inline":false,"local_path":"writeups/writeup_00.html"}],"sources":[{"origin":"hackropole","url":"https://hackropole.fr/fr/challenges/web/fcsc2026-web-10-fast-fisher/","license":{"spdx_id":"etalab-2.0","confidence":1.0,"redistributable":true,"note":"Hackropole content under Licence Ouverte 2.0"},"is_official":true}],"license":{"spdx_id":"etalab-2.0","confidence":1.0,"redistributable":true,"note":"Hackropole content under Licence Ouverte 2.0"},"content_fingerprint":